data.description:
"Live in the Heart of Denver!" Enjoy breathtaking views & an unbeatable location! This modern & stylish condo boasts stunning vistas of the city skyline. Step inside & you'll find gleaming wood floors guiding you through the spacious open-concept kitchen. The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, sleek slab granite countertops, a beautifully tiled backsplash, ample counter space, & a convenient island with seating. The living has crown molding and is bathed in natural light and access to generously sized balcony, perfect for outdoor dining while gazing at the city lights in the evening. This home offers a dedicated dining area, a rare home office with built-in features, & two spacious bedrooms with French Doors, each large enough to accommodate a king-size bed. Both bedrooms also offer lovely views & ample closet space, a unique feature in city living. The 2 full bathrooms have been tastefully updated with designer tiles and fixtures, ensuring that this home is move-in ready. The HOA amenities are impressive, including an outdoor pool and hot tub with grills & a courtyard, a movie theater, a fully equipped gym, a bike room with storage, a business center, tanning beds, & a beautiful clubhouse for entertaining. This unit comes with 2 garage parking spaces & "3 storage units" conveniently located on the first floor. You'll love the unbeatable location, just blocks away from the light rail, Santa Fe Arts District, Cherry Creek Path, & all the fantastic dining, shopping, & nightlife options that Downtown Denver has to offer!  (Please see www.thelincolndenver.com/amenities for more info)

**** Seller has FHA ASSUMABLE LOAN @ 2.875% and pay the differ of purchase price to loan.

*Seller is offering $$ towards for 2/1 buydown rate program "not on the assumable deal" 

*Property qualifies for Deerfield Homeownership Fund (in documents)- John Collins PNC Bank 720.270.5646 -NMLS#669008
